'''藍松雞屬'''（{{lang|la|''Dendragapus''}}）是[[鸡形目|鸡形目]][[松雞亞科|松雞亞科]]以下的一個屬，包括兩個關係非常密切，過往曾以為是同一種的物種，分別為：較淺色的[[:en:Dusky_Grouse|Dusky Grouse]] (''Dendragapus obscurus'')及較深色的[[:en:Sooty_Grouse|Sooty Grouse]] (''Dendragapus fuliginosus'')<ref name="AOU">{{cite journal | last=Banks | first=R. C. | coauthors=Cicero, C., Dunn, J. L., Kratter, A. W., Rasmussen, P. C., Remsen, J. V., Jr., Rising, J. D., & Stotz, D. F. | title=Forty-seventh Supplement to the American Ornithologists' Union Check-list of North American Birds | journal=The Auk | year=2006 | volume=123 | issue=3 | pages=926–936 | url=http://www.aou.org/checklist/suppl/AOU_checklist_suppl_47.pdf | accessdate=2007-09-16 | doi=10.1642/0004-8038(2006)123[926:FSTTAO]2.0.CO;2 | issn=0004-8038 | archive-date=2015-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226015415/http://www.aou.org/checklist/suppl/AOU_checklist_suppl_47.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。這兩個種過往都被稱為「藍松雞」或「蓝镰翅鸡」。此外，[[:en:Spruce_Grouse|Spruce Grouse]]及[[西伯利亞松雞|西伯利亞松雞]]過往亦曾被劃進藍松雞屬。

== 描述 ==
藍松雞屬的兩個品種在[[松雞|松雞]]當中都屬於大個頭，棲息於[[北太平洋|北太平洋]]兩岸的[[北美洲|北美洲]]及[[歐亞大陸|歐亞大陸]]高原地區。Sooty Grouse可於[[太平洋海岸山脈|太平洋海岸山脈]]及[[內華達山脈_(美國)|美國內華達山脈]]發現，而Dusky Grouse則棲息於[[洛磯山脈|洛磯山脈]]<ref name=hbw>del Hoyo, J., Elliott, A., & Sargatal, J., eds. (1994). ''Handbook of the Birds of the World'' 2: 401-402. Lynx Edicions, Barcelona ISBN 84-87334-15-6.</ref><ref name="Zwickel">{{cite book  | last = Zwickel  | first = Fred C.  | coauthors = Bendell, James F.  | title = Blue Grouse: Their Biology and Natural History  | publisher = NRC Research Press  | year = 2004  | location = Ottawa  | pages =   | url = http://pubs.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca/eng/books/books/9780660192710.html  | isbn = 978-0-660-19271-0  | deadurl = yes  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071225163347/http://pubs.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca/eng/books/books/9780660192710.html  | archivedate = 2007-12-25  | access-date = 2012-03-27  }}</ref><ref name=Sibley>{{cite book | author=[[David_Allen_Sibley|Sibley, D.]] | title=[[The_Sibley_Guide_to_Birds|The Sibley Guide to Birds]] | publisher=Knopf | year=2000 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/sibleyguidetobir00sibl_0/page/143 143] | isbn=0-679-45122-6}}</ref>。 

== 化石 ==
''Dendragapus gilli''是一種於美國西部及中西部發現的[[晚更新世|晚更新世]][[化石|化石]]品種；亦有另外一種於[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]][[萊克縣_(俄勒岡州)|萊克縣 (俄勒岡州)]][[化石湖|化石湖]]發現的品種，過往曾被劃分為''Palaeotetrix''屬<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Condor/files/issues/v069n01/p0024-p0027.pdf |title=Pleistocene birds from Fossil Lake, Oregon |journal=The Condor |issue=69 |pages=24-27 |year=1967 |language=en |author= |access-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307225519/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Condor/files/issues/v069n01/p0024-p0027.pdf |archive-date=2008-03-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，現時都是藍松雞屬的一員。

